org.opensha.gmm

Enum GMM

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GMM>
      • org.opensha.gmm.GMM
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GMM>

    public enum GMM
extends Enum<GMM>
    Ground motion model (GMM) identifiers that can supply instances of various ground motion model implementations. Single or corporate authored models are identified as NAME_YR_FLAVOR; multi-author models as INITIALS_YR_FLAVOR. FLAVOR is only used for those models with region specific implementations or other variants.
    Author:
    Peter Powers
